### Task Management API - Task Endpoints
### Base URL: http://localhost:8080

### Create Task
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Complete project documentation",
  "description": "Write comprehensive documentation for the task management API",
  "status": "pending"
}

###

### Create Task - Minimal (only title required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Review code changes"
}

###

### Get All Tasks (User sees only their tasks, Admin sees all)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Tasks with Pagination
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?page=1&limit=5
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Tasks with Status Filter
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Tasks with Search
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?search=documentation
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Tasks with Multiple Filters
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks?page=1&limit=10&status=in_progress&search=project
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Get Task by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

###

### Update Task - Full Update
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "Updated task title",
  "description": "Updated description with more details",
  "status": "in_progress"
}

###

### Update Task - Partial Update (only status)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "status": "completed"
}

###

### Update Task - Partial Update (only title)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "title": "New task title"
}

###

### Delete Task
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/tasks/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE

